Interface SubQueryExpression<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - return type of subquery
    All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExtendedSubQueryExpression<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface SubQueryExpression<T>
extends Expression<T>
    SubQueryExpression represents a sub query. The actual construction of a subquery is done via an Detachable instance.
